00:19:47.890 --> 00:19:48.770
Esta noche,

00:19:50.450 --> 00:19:51.970
confiemos en esto por ahora.

00:19:53.130 --> 00:19:53.810
Dame la mano.

00:19:57.730 --> 00:19:58.850
En mi vida,

00:20:02.130 --> 00:20:03.440
espero estar contigo

00:20:05.450 --> 00:20:06.890
